ChiKareGo2 — by Giles Booth
A true 16px-grid pixel recreation of Susan Kare's Chicago.

Source: https://www.pentacom.jp/pentacom/bitfontmaker2/gallery/?id=3780 (BitFontMaker2)
License: Creative Commons Attribution (CC BY) — verified on the gallery page 2026-07-19.
Obligation: visible credit "Font: ChiKareGo2 by Giles Booth" on every surface that embeds it.

Files: ChiKareGo2.ttf (as downloaded), ChiKareGo2.woff2 (fonttools conversion, no glyph changes).
Pixel-grid rule: crisp ONLY at 16px and integer multiples (32/48). Never render off-grid.
